OL,3,CGuernsey nurses and firefighters agree
OL,4,Cpay rise
OL,6,FHundreds of emergency services staff
OL,7,Fin Guernsey have agreed to a 3.7% pay
OL,8,Frise.
OL,10,FIt will be backdated to January,
OL,11,Ffollowing an agreement between the
OL,12,FPolicy and Resources Committee (P&R)
OL,13,Fand unions representing healthcare
OL,14,Fworkers, including nurses, on 'Agenda
OL,15,Ffor Change' contracts, plus Guernsey
OL,16,FFire and Rescue.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
