PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779127867
OL,3,CGuernsey nurses and firefighters agree
OL,4,Cpay rise
OL,6,FHowever, representatives for several
OL,7,Fother groups, including hospital
OL,8,Fconsultants, prison officers, and
OL,9,FAirport Fire and Rescue Service (AFRS)
OL,10,Femployees, are yet to agree terms.
OL,12,FIt means across the public sector,
OL,13,Faround 15% have not yet accepted pay
OL,14,Foffers for 2026.
OL,16,FOn those outstanding discussions, P&R
OL,17,Fsays AFRS are currently balloting
OL,18,Ftheir members and the other sectors
OL,19,Fshould have revised proposals in early
OL,20,FJune.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779127867
OL,3,CGuernsey nurses and firefighters agree
OL,4,Cpay rise
OL,6,FThe Committee adds: "Naturally, we
OL,7,Fwould like all pay deals to be agreed
OL,8,Fas soon as possible, not least so that
OL,9,Findividuals can benefit from their
OL,10,Frevised pay, but we are satisfied that
OL,11,Fprogress is being made."
OL,13,FIt hopes to conclude the remaining
OL,14,Fdeals by the end of June, with pay
OL,15,Foffers for 2027 set to be discussed
OL,16,Ffrom July once the latest inflation
OL,17,Frate is published.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
